>> Array of tool names
env @config with { tools: ["read", "write"] } [...]

>> Comma-separated string
env @config with { tools: "read, write" } [...]

>> Wildcard for all tools
env @config with { tools: "*" } [...]

>> Object keys as tool names
var @subset = { read: @readTool, write: @writeTool }
env @config with { tools: @subset } [...]